text: Understand that it's peak hour during my order. They forgot to give chili sauce, but its ok cause i have it at home. But chicken chop without sauce.. Spoil the mood. ðŸ™„

Damn slow. Took 30mins to get my order and i order tom yam fried rice. Cashier and cook can be seen taking their own sweet time, no urgency hehe-haha when there are many orders to fulfill. Frequented this place a few times for lunch, cashier no sense of awareness. If you have abundance of time to spare the food is alright but otherwise better not if you want efficient service.

Ordered chicken cutlet w fried rice and seafood beehoon.
Chicken cutlet not bad , fried rice no wok hay and bland.
Seafood beehoon can taste alot msg , passable. Tats all to say !
The fish had some pink color inside, lacked tartar sauce, and I even found a rotten tomato. Really disappointing experience.
